---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
	<main class="privacy-page">
		<header>
			<p class="eyebrow">Data protection</p>
			<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
			<p class="lead">
				CogNeuroEdu processes personal information in accordance with Regulation (EU) 2016/679 (GDPR) and Spanish
				legislation applicable to the Universidad Nacional de Educación a Distancia.
			</p>
		</header>

		<section>
			<h2>Controller</h2>
			<p>
				CogNeuroEdu Research Group · Faculty of Education (UNED). C/ Juan del Rosal 14, 28040 Madrid, Spain.
				Emails:
				<a href="mailto:cogneuroedu@edu.uned.es">cogneuroedu@edu.uned.es</a>,
				<a href="mailto:mt.m.aragoneses@edu.uned.es">mt.m.aragoneses@edu.uned.es</a>. Phone:
				<a href="tel:+34913987384">+34 91 398 73 84</a>.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Purpose</h2>
			<p>
				Data gathered through forms, emails, or participation initiatives is used to answer queries, coordinate research
				actions, manage events, and send communications related to CogNeuroEdu's scientific activity. No automated
				decision-making or commercial profiling is performed.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Legal basis</h2>
			<p>
				The lawful basis is the public interest in scientific research and the academic/contractual relationship with
				collaborators. When explicit consent is required, it will be requested clearly and may be withdrawn at any time.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Recipients</h2>
			<p>
				Data is stored on UNED infrastructure and shared only with partner institutions when a specific research or
				transfer agreement exists.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Retention</h2>
			<p>
				Information is preserved while necessary to address the original request and meet UNED's legal obligations. Once
				these periods expire, data is blocked or anonymized according to university procedures.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section>
			<h2>Rights</h2>
			<p>
				You may exercise your rights of access, rectification, erasure, objection, restriction, or portability by emailing
				<a href="mailto:cogneuroedu@edu.uned.es">cogneuroedu@edu.uned.es</a>. You may also lodge a complaint with the
				Spanish Data Protection Agency if you consider that the processing does not comply with current regulations.
			</p>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	.privacy-page {
		padding: calc(var(--nav-height, 72px) + 3rem) var(--page-padding, clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem)) 3rem;
		max-width: 960px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		box-sizing: border-box;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	header .eyebrow {
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.25em;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		color: #666;
		margin: 0;
	}

	header h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 3rem);
		margin: 0.5rem 0;
	}

	.lead {
		font-size: 1.05rem;
		color: #3a3a3a;
		margin: 0;
	}

	section h2 {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
	}

	p {
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #1f1f1f;
	}

	a {
		color: inherit;
		font-weight: 600;
	}
</style>
